org.pepstock.charba.client.commons

Class JavaScriptObjectContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.JavaScriptObjectContainer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractItem, AnimationItem, BaseBoxItem, ChartBackgroundColorOptions, ChartContainer, ChartNode, Context, Data, DataPoint, Dataset, DatasetItem, DatasetMetaItem, DatasetViewItem, DisplayFormats, LegendItem, Plugins, ScalesNode, SizeItem, TickItem, TooltipBodyItem, TooltipItem, TooltipItemArray, TooltipLabelColor, TooltipLabelColor, TooltipModel, TooltipNode, TooltipsCallbacks, UpdateConfiguration

    public class JavaScriptObjectContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains a GWT JavaScript object. This is used for all configuration items for CHART.JS.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
    See Also:
    GenericJavaScriptObject
